<view class="container">
  <view class="card section panel">
    <view class="title-lg">自定义尺寸</view>
    <view class="text-muted">适用于特殊尺寸证件照、报名表照片、签证照片等需求</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card section panel">
    <view class="field">
      <text class="label">宽度（毫米）</text>
      <input class="input" type="digit" placeholder="请输入宽度" value="{{widthMm}}" bindinput="onWidthInput" />
    </view>
    <view class="field">
      <text class="label">高度（毫米）</text>
      <input class="input" type="digit" placeholder="请输入高度" value="{{heightMm}}" bindinput="onHeightInput" />
    </view>
    <view class="field">
      <text class="label">背景颜色</text>
      <color-picker value="{{color}}" bind:change="onColorChange"></color-picker>
    </view>
    <view class="text-muted tip">请填写实际需要的照片宽度和高度；若不确定尺寸，建议优先使用首页固定场景模板。</view>
  </view>

  <primary-button text="下一步" bind:tap="nextStep"></primary-button>
</view>
